channel.title: Version 5.23 :: Cap'n Hugo Relearrrn Theme
channel.description: 5.23.0 (2023-11-03) Change Change Wit' 0.120.0 th' author sett'ns move into th' [params] array 'n yer hugo.toml. Because this collides wit' th' previous way, th' theme expected author informat'n, it now adheres t' Cap'n Hugo standards an' prints out a warning dur'n built if someth'n be wrong.
